column5: Hi everyone  I've been directed to this site by mike Rousseau. I fish with him a lot and it sounds like a great site. And I'm really pumped for the online tournament. I fish for whatever is biting that time of year and always willing to try new fish.
Took long enough....  Here's a pic of you so everyone can see you
Welcome aboard.  I like that fish !!!!!!
Nice fish but your no Steel Bunny I guess we should welcome you anyway. LOL
Welcome aboard. Looking forward to some reports.
Welcome!  Who's the dude holding you?
Good to have you aboard & nice catch !!
Sweet fish! Welcome to the group..You will have many laughs and meet many good folks along the way..
Welcome!  Who's the dude holding you? LMAO!
Nice intro.  From the way your holding that fish it looks like its not your first trophy.
Welcome aboard,looks like you have a good fish mate.Looking forward to your reports!!!You'll like it hear.
